Text: Heinz ISDAam forwarding you the information of the contact at Heinz who requested a copy of their ISDA Will you please forward her a copy of the ISDA via overnight mail or fax today She has requested a copy by Monday May Please let me know if you have any questions Thanks Dewann Weltmer Heinz North America PO Box Pittsburgh PA email Ph Fx

FW SwapsMessage From Weltmer Dewann HNA ENRON mailtoIMCEANOTESWeltmerCDewannHNACDewannEWeltmer hjheinzEcomE NRONcom Sent Thursday May AM To Bonner Elliot Subject RE Swaps Hello Elliot Sorry I couldnt get back with you until now Either I am out of the office or in meetings all day Last we spoke you were going to send me a copy of the previous agreed upon ISDA between Heinz and Enron I believe you wanted our legal contact but is there anyway you can send the copy to my attention I would like to have a copy for my files We have not made a decision yet on linerboard swaps I have a meeting with my General Manager on Monday PM and hope to know more Can you please send me a copy of the ISDA prior to Monday PM Thanks Dewann Weltmer Heinz NA Procurement Packaging phone fax Original Message From mailto Sent Thursday May AM To Subject RE Swaps Have you made a decision on this swap yet Please let me know either way Thanks Original Message From Weltmer Dewann HNA ENRON mailtoIMCEANOTESWeltmerCDewannHNACDewannEWeltmer hjheinzEcomE NRONcom Sent Tuesday May AM To Bonner Elliot Subject Swaps Hi Elliott I talked with Corby and today we have an offer around ton for years tons Can you provide a better offer that we could discuss Thanks Dewann Weltmer Heinz NA Procurement Packaging phone fax

Unilever Legal Contactleft you a voicemail about Unilever earlier I am going to forward your number to their legal contact Peter Harwich He will be in contact with any legal questions I met with Michael Lagamma and Jim ORourke of Unilever in New Jersey to discuss the details of the transaction yesterday Please let me know if you have any questions Thanks
